===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|sa|मण्डप}}, {{m|sa|मण्टप|tr=maṇḍapa, maṇṭapa||pavilion, mandapa}}, a non-native word likely from the same source as {{m|sa|मठ||hut, hermit's cottage}}. Probably derived via {{der|en|hi|मंडप}} or another New Indo-Aryan language.

